OL,3,CMajor HSBC office vandalised
OL,5,FA major HSBC office in Sheffield has
OL,6,Fbeen vandalised overnight.
OL,8,FThe bank's IT hub on Grosvenor Street
OL,9,Fhad its windows smashed while its
OL,10,Fwalls were graffitied with pro-
OL,11,FPalestine messages.
OL,13,FSouth Yorkshire Police say it is
OL,14,Finvestigating after receiving reports
OL,15,Fof criminal damage on Wellington
OL,16,FStreet at 2.13am on Monday 2 March.
OL,18,FAmong the graffiti, "DROP ELBIT"
OL,19,Fseemingly references Elbit Systems
OL,20,Fwhich sells military equipment.
