OL,3,CMajor HSBC office vandalised
OL,5,FThe police added: "It is reported a
OL,6,Fgroup of people wearing face coverings
OL,7,Fvandalised the building by spraying it
OL,8,Fwith paint and smashing windows before
OL,9,Fleaving on foot in the direction of
OL,10,FPound's Park.
OL,12,F"Enquiries into the incident are
OL,13,Fongoing and anyone with any
OL,14,Finformation is asked to contact us."
